import SVG1 from '../../images/svg-1.svg'
import SVG2 from '../../images/svg-2.svg'

export const homeObjOne = {
    id: 'about',
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Machine Learning',
    headline: 'Guess the species',
    description: 'This webpage uses a machine learning model to guess the species of an iris flower taking into consideration some input parameters.',
    buttonLabel: 'Get started',
    imgStart: false,
    img: SVG1,
    alt: 'Car',
    dark: false,
    primary: false,
    darkText: false
}

export const homeObjTwo = {
    id: 'discover',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Premium bank',
    headline: 'Unlimited transactions with zero fees.',
    description: 'Get access to our exclusive app that allows you to send unlimited transactions without getting charged any fees.',
    buttonLabel: 'Get started',
    imgStart: false,
    img: SVG2,
    alt: 'Car',
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
}

export const homeObjThree = {
    id: 'discover',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Our team',
    headline: 'The whole is other than the sum of the parts',
    description: '"None of us, including me, ever do great things. But we can all do small things, with great love, and together we can do something wonderful." – Mother Teresa',
    buttonLabel: 'Get started',
    imgStart: false,
    img: SVG2,
    alt: 'Car',
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
}
